refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraycal_from_jd intjd intcalendar
cal_from_jd Konvertiert den Julian-Tag gegeben in jd in ein Datum des calendar. Unterstützte calendar Werte sind CAL_GREGORIAN, CAL_JULIAN, CAL_JEWISH und CAL_FRENCH.

&reftitle.examples;
cal_from_jd Beispiel
<?php $today = unixtojd(mktime(0, 0, 0, 8, 16, 2003)); print_r(cal_from_jd($today, CAL_GREGORIAN)); ?>
&example.outputs;
Array ( [date] => 8/16/2003 [month] => 8 [day] => 16 [year] => 2003 [dow] => 6 [abbrevdayname] => Sat [dayname] => Saturday [abbrevmonth] => Aug [monthname] => August )
